cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with improving the training of convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also proposes a method for evaluating and replacing specific convolutional filters, which could be considered a form of optimization (cs.AI) or natural language processing (cs.CL) if applied to text-based models.
